qreg other_share_Y1 ln_aksje i.emp_cat i.zip_cat i.Chair_gender_cat i.SFACT_bin i.RegYear if NACE_section != 16 & NACE_section != 21, quantile(0.5)
bsqreg other_share_Y1 ln_aksje i.emp_cat i.zip_cat i.Chair_gender_cat i.SFACT_bin i.RegYear if NACE_section != 16 & NACE_section != 21, quantile(0.5) reps(200)
* ==========================================================
