* Try bsqreg without NACE (non-fatal)
capture noisily bsqreg other_share_Y5 ln_aksje i.emp_cat i.zip_cat i.Chair_gender_cat i.SFACT_bin i.RegYear if NACE_section != 16 & NACE_section != 21, quantile(0.5) reps(200)
if _rc {
di as text "NOTE: bsqreg (no NACE) did not converge for other_share_Y5 (rc=" _rc "). Proceeding with descriptive evidence only."
}
* Try qreg without NACE (non-fatal)
capture noisily qreg other_share_Y5 ln_aksje i.emp_cat i.zip_cat i.Chair_gender_cat i.SFACT_bin i.RegYear if NACE_section != 16 & NACE_section != 21, quantile(0.5)
if _rc {
di as text "NOTE: qreg (no NACE) did not converge / VCE failed for other_share_Y5 (rc=" _rc "). Proceeding with descriptive evidence only."
}
* Internal diagnostic only: OLS with robust SE retained to verify NACE inclusion did not cause the sample loss observed in the median specification. Not referenced in main text.
