* ============================================
* Tables D9-D15: Nested Cox models, strict failure - SFACT_bin coefficient evolution from M1 (sustainability factor only) through M7 (full specification, Table 13)
* zip_cat and Chair_gender_cat entered as separate models
* ============================================
preserve
drop if missing(NACE_section)
drop if NACE_section == 16 | NACE_section == 21
stset surv_time, failure(failed_strict)
estimates clear

* ----- M1: SFACT_bin only -----
stcox i.SFACT_bin
estimates store M1
* ----- M2: + NACE_section -----
stcox i.SFACT_bin i.NACE_section
